# Ticketing Stack - Skill Manifest
# Version: 1.0.0
# Format: path/to/skill:version (or path/to/skill for latest)
#
# Bundled with the ticketing agent: everything needed to reliably create,
# update, and verify GitHub issues/PRs/labels from automation and subagents.

# GitHub CLI operations (issue/PR/label) with pre-flight auth verification
universal/collaboration/gh-cli

# Conventional commits, branching, PR hygiene for ticket-linked work
universal/collaboration/git-workflow

# Never report a ticket as created/closed without verifying the result
universal/debugging/verification-before-completion
